This paper analyzes the activity of extreme right groups on Twitter, focusing on network representations and topic analysis. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Social and Behavioral Sciences (cs.SOC), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
